There were 2 problems in total here:
 1. spring-boot 2.6.6 wasn&#39;t compatible with spring-context 5.2.5.RELEASE
 2. Spring has moved support for netflix-zuul to maintenance mode, so Zuul wouldn&#39;t work with 2.6.6

Solution:
Downgrade spring-boot to 2.4.12 (2.4.x) for Zuul support, and upgrade the spring version to 5.3.18 so to prevent exposure to the RCE vulnerability. Also, use a spring-cloud-starter-bootstrap 3.0.1 for sping-context incompatibility. remove the spring-context dependency.

